      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the salmon is in the oven, peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> pak choi</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and cut in half, separating the <strong>white bases </strong>and <strong>green tops</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
