    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> pak choi green tops</strong> and your<strong> soy sauce </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the pak choi green tops have wilted</p><p>Sprinkle your<strong> toasted sesame seeds </strong>over<strong> </strong>the<strong> </strong>wilted pak choi – this is your <strong>sesame pak choi</strong></p>",
